			<p>
				Membership is complimentary, but subject to status. Applicants are asked to complete a short FT registration process and then tell us (just a bit) about themselves.
			</p>
			<p>
				Please note - the Long Room is aimed at professional market participants who understand the complexities of the financial instruments discussed, together with the attendant risks. The content is not suitable for retail clients.
			</p>
            <p>
